<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1096962' id='t-1096962'>and look at the world from a different perspective.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1102970' id='t-1102970'>And when you see mountains,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1105415' id='t-1105415'>remember mountains can be moved.</span>
